phora, Samsung, Urban Outfitters and also appeared on the covers of Cosmopolitan and Blazer. When she was 16 Dar was accepted into \"Alon School For the Arts\", considered one of the top schools of its kind in the country. While there Dar studied acting and was considered very promising. At the age of eighteen Dar was drafted for the Israeli Defense Force and served for three years. During this time she also worked as both a model and actress. Dar's first acting project was the lead role in Nickelodeon's \"The Greenhouse.\" The show received many Israeli awards during its four season run and was later syndicated to Nickelodeon UK. Following the success of \"The Greenhouse\" Dar was cast as Nohar Shiff on \"Scarred\", an action series that has millions of fans and is considered to be a smash hit. With this momentum Dar was able to land the lead role on the internationally award- winning drama \"Hostages.\" In 2015 she starred in her first feature film \"Ibiza\" which was shot in Spain.","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"דר זוזובסקי","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дар Зузовски","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"pa","name":"ਪੰਜਾਬੀ","english_name":"Punjabi","data":{"biography":"","name":"ਦਰ ਜ਼ੁਜ਼ੋਵਸਕੀ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"دار زوزوفسکی","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IE","iso_639_1":"ga","name":"Gaeilge","english_name":"Irish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"دار زوزوفسكي","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"NL","iso_639_1":"nl","name":"Nederlands","english_name":"Dutch","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"ca","name":"Català","english_name":"Catalan","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AL","iso_639_1":"sq","name":"shqip","english_name":"Albanian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dar Zuzovsky","primary":false}}]}},"person_2163142_translations":{"at":1774698740518,"data":{"id":2163142,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zeng Mengxue","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"曾梦雪，1994年10月12日出生于四川成都，中国内地女演员。\n\n2011年，出演古装喜剧《公主出山》女一号孙静格格 [，并由此开始演艺生涯。2016年1月，凭借古装武侠网络剧《苏染染追夫记》中的杜瑶冰一角受到关注 ；同年，参演由金晨、王大陆主演的网络季播剧《鬼吹灯之牧野诡事》，饰演神仙眼一角 。2017年，出演爱情电影《前任3：再见前任》。","name":"曾梦雪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Η Zeng Meng Xue είναι μια Κινέζα ηθοποιός που γεννήθηκε στις 12 Οκτωβρίου 1994, στο Sichuan της Κίνας. Σπούδασε σε μια σχολή κινηματογράφου και τηλεόρασης με έδρα το Πεκίνο, την οποία διευθύνει η Κινέζα ηθοποιός Fan Bing Bing, και έκανε το ντεμπούτο της στην κωμωδία περιόδου του 2012 «Princess Reinstated». Συνέχισε με την εμφάνιση στο τηλεοπτικό δράμα \"Su Ran's Husband Hunting Journey\" (2016) και έκανε το ντεμπούτο της στον κινηματογράφο στο \"The Ex-Files 3: The Return of the Exes\" (2017), παίζοντας έναν από τους τέσσερις βασικούς χαρακτήρες. Πιο πρόσφατα, εμφανίστηκε στα δράματα «Hi! My Ex» (2018) και «Cupid of the Chou Dynasty» (2019).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"曾夢雪，生於1994年10月12日，四川成都人，中國女演員。2011年，首次演出古裝喜劇《公主出山》，擔任女主角孫靜格格，自此開始她的演藝生涯。","name":"Zeng Mengxue","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"曾夢雪，生於 1994 年 10 月 12 日，四川成都人，中國女演員。2011 年，首次演出古裝喜劇《公主出山》，擔任女主角孫靜格格，自此開始她的演藝生涯。","name":"曾夢雪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Цзэн Мэн Сюэ","primary":false}}]}},"tv_285739_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774698747431,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/fqWXGP79tEMAyLKW0wkJLbKSP61.jpg","created_by":[{"id":5283139,"credit_id":"69a9dc236a287ba770e8cba3","name":"Julia May Jonas","original_name":"Julia May Jonas","gender":1,"profile_path":null}],"episode_run_time":[],"first_air_date":"2026-03-05","genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81737584","id":285739,"in_production":false,"languages":["en"],"last_air_date":"2026-03-05","last_episode_to_air":{"id":6891029,"name":"Chống Diễn Giải","overview":"Chuyến đi nghỉ dưỡng ở nông thôn trở nên phức tạp khi M và Vlad suy ngẫm về sự nghiệp viết lách, hôn nhân và tương lai đầy bất trắc của họ.","vote_average":7,"vote_count":1,"air_date":"2026-03-05","episode_number":8,"episode_type":"finale","production_code":"","runtime":32,"season_number":1,"show_id":285739,"still_path":"/tJaxomFgZohEpg4RRhNVVE08OWV.jpg"},"name":"Vladimir","next_episode_to_air":null,"networks":[{"id":213,"logo_path":"/wwemzKWzjKYJFfCeiB57q3r4Bcm.png","name":"Netflix","origin_country":""}],"number_of_episodes":8,"number_of_seasons":1,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Vladimir","overview":"Khi giáo sư tiếng Anh nọ trở nên ám ảnh về người đồng nghiệp mới điển trai, cuộc hôn nhân và sự nghiệp vốn đã phức tạp của cô bị đẩy vào hỗn loạn tột cùng.","popularity":2